        <h2>My Hobbies</h2>
        <ul>
            <li>Cooking - Food from many cultures. I'm not very picky.'</li>
            <li>Sports - Soccer, Basketball, Football</li>
            <li>Lifting - I enjoy lifting and have lifted since junior year of hs</li>
            <li>Music - I mostly listen to r&b, rap, afrobeats, etc. (Pretty diverse music taste)</li>
            <li>Anime - My favorites are One Piece, Vinland Saga, Attack on Titan</li>
        </ul>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
